    <h2 class="node-title node-glossary-title"><a href="/glossary/shallot">Shallot</a></h2>
    <span class="fonetic text-style-alt">shal-lot</span>
    <p>Related to the onion (as opposed to being a younger version of it), shallots grow in clusters atâ€¦</p>
    </article>
